  <data name="PrivateKeyExportWarning" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Exporting your private key exposes full control over your wallet assets. If the private key is compromised, anyone can transfer your assets, and this cannot be reversed or recovered.

Make sure to perform this action in a secure, offline environment where no one can observe you. Do not take screenshots, photos, or copy it to chat apps, email, or cloud storage. Never share your private key with anyone.

Please note: We do not store or manage your private key. If it is lost, forgotten, or damaged, it cannot be recovered.

After exporting, store it securely and ensure your current environment is safe.</value>
